{"tid":144392,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"癲狗系列 - 蘿蔔糕","createTime":"2017-03-05T11:29:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-07T04:48:28.000Z","uid":74981,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4da7c323714ba65a5d7362dbf7b4b250cb2eb28e","tid":144392,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T11:29:35.000Z","msg":"材料:<br />\n6斤半蘿蔔 (去皮，刨絲)<br />\n1斤粘米粉<br />\n臘腸6條 (切粒，炒香)<br />\n元貝，蝦米 (浸過，king乾水，炒香)<br />\n冬菇 (唔記得浸)<br />\n<br />\n1. 落油炒蘿蔔絲<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/1c09e3d0771fea329620a604c37e705f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F1c09e3d0771fea329620a604c37e705f.jpg&h=16e2ae70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 炒到出哂水謝哂皮，落臘腸粒，蝦米粒，元貝粒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/1def0bc3d7bf6a5a1074b53c7d2b59ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F1def0bc3d7bf6a5a1074b53c7d2b59ce.jpg&h=0b13e7b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 等d味出哂黎，開始調味，糖2茶匙，白胡椒粉1.5茶匙，鹽1.5茶匙，攪勻煮一煮。<br />\n<br />\n4. 落粘米粉，分批落，唔好一次落咁多，如果唔係好難攪勻。落一次粉，用獲剷背掃平掃勻，再翻一下d蘿蔔漿，再用獲剷背掃平掃勻，重覆至所有粉用完為止。<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/f04c78ac6ea383cfcf8c89ce9e64a90c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Ff04c78ac6ea383cfcf8c89ce9e64a90c.jpg&h=8a8c3d44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/00047fcda445a23a0ed8fa18ed473674.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F00047fcda445a23a0ed8fa18ed473674.jpg&h=09a949a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/569d38cddeba6c2d1f6fed185d1e017e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F569d38cddeba6c2d1f6fed185d1e017e.jpg&h=e5ce055f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 上碟，水滾蒸40分鐘<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/284cd6c89dfaefa95b421abe662accbf.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F284cd6c89dfaefa95b421abe662accbf.jpeg&h=36a278d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 完成。蒸好已經同屋企人忍唔住食左一半，好味既蘿蔔糕，果然係蒸好食過煎既，不過我都會留番d聽日煎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/bbf94fd9030ecc332ddb4201c1a70516.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fbbf94fd9030ecc332ddb4201c1a70516.jpg&h=f03a97cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 如果想個質感滑d，可以加鷹粟粉，不過我冇加，因為我覺得咁樣已經夠好食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac57ef259c0e2c504d742a7124d1c10db405f1cb","tid":144392,"uid":2766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T11:31:46.000Z","msg":"呢次識玩 圖文教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"897f4d76472af396b73912b322e443f6c89696ab","tid":144392,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T11:51:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢次識玩 圖文教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前成日都係咁，不過之前有巴打要求拍片我咪玩下囉。。拍得片又懶打字 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ad351fc1119a95afdfc6ed0c4522af42acc3e92","tid":144392,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T11:53:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ae0fcb21439da0d982c07c283f9853e2825dc66","tid":144392,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T12:01:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"977ed36b0141064d99552a2678e15b695ec038d9","tid":144392,"uid":63675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T12:22:42.000Z","msg":"最愛蘿蔔糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff7e7fb87169aae26abd3c6bf6d5e08333c4e841","tid":144392,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T12:23:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最愛蘿蔔糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce0aa80344313c799aa22f27258f415890868858","tid":144392,"uid":10011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T12:25:18.000Z","msg":"過年食咗十幾底都未厭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b238379331e70c32ce761f52ab9ccf58e99b98","tid":144392,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T12:35:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過年食咗十幾底都未厭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb1e452ab8a5b5fc84b3b764b78f37edbf862c95","tid":144392,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T12:35:56.000Z","msg":"no good <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaa3e57a37edb1815e9176a6a3920fd253abe2c3","tid":144392,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T12:37:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>no good <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n指教下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c5273fcc435568520ea29c4082bfa50e4f623bd","tid":144392,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T12:39:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>no good <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n指教下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces