s.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f869faae3ccf5282b4a63756d39adde7eb64ac","tid":144392,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T13:30:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好足料喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我媽中意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3854a4c65c57f2dd68e77346a2dfde3e918ae848","tid":144392,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T13:30:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我同你相反<br />\n我覺得蘿蔔糕要煎先好食<br />\n年糕就要蒸嘅好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23495f95c2a71cc9e1b39d7d7fe28c7b5be8f644","tid":144392,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T13:31:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>狗巴強勢回歸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nd藥食哂我又會發癲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b50db70873936456e4167ce5bdb4b8295e1bb8f","tid":144392,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T13:31:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我同你相反<br />\n我覺得蘿蔔糕要煎先好食<br />\n年糕就要蒸嘅好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n炒先正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nxo醬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e5daca8b132aecda9aa7c7c0011288d8eaea4a0","tid":144392,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T13:31:35.000Z","msg":"用左幾多時間"},{"pid":"6d6ad520cc6b58093c3afc9558f430a1a878442d","tid":144392,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T13:34:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用左幾多時間</blockquote><br />\n刨皮加刨絲20分鐘，煮約20至30分鐘，蒸每底40分鐘，共兩底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d5dc52fc6c22218710b4a0be1038284698f6ec","tid":144392,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T13:42:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>no good <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n指教下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為我唔鍾意食蘿蔔糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我口味好怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}